descriptionHtml:
CannaBuzz is a cannabis community platform, a social video & picture app with much more! Created by censored content creators who wanted a safe platform for legal cannabis.

Whether you enjoy the occasional joint, you're a grower or strain breeder, a Ganjapreneur, a #smokeweedallday follower, or a believer in whole-plant medicine - and everything in between! - CannaBuzz is here for you.

●Curate your Feed● This is your cannabis social network. Follow your favorite accounts to get the latest and dankest in your feed.

●Share the Love● Share images, up to 5-minute length videos, or text posts (w/links!) to your feed. You can even broadcast live-video!

●Groups & Chat● Join groups based on your interests and chat with members. Meet other fellow cannabis fans and check out their profiles. Create a private chat with a friend!

●Safe & Secure● CannaBuzz was created by an experienced team with a background in both community management and as cannabis advocates. We built this place because we believe that the global cannabis community deserves a safe space online.

●Available on the Web ● Visit our website from your desktop computer, share your CannaBuzz content links with the world!

We’re a passionate team of cannabis advocates that are proud to provide a place for anyone to find their corner of the cannabis community. CannaBuzz is a friendly place, filled with creative and passionate people. We're like a Weedstagram ;)

We're a safe place for WeedTubers, Weedstagrammers, Dabbers, or those just hoping to put themselves' on the Weed Map!

Stay Connected with your favorite Weed App!

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/cannabuzzapp

Whether you enjoy the occasional joint, you're a grower or strain breeder, a Ganjapreneur, a #smokeweedallday follower, or a believer in whole-plant medicine - and everything in between! - CannaBuzz is here for you.

●Curate your Feed● This is your cannabis social network. Follow your favorite accounts to get the latest and dankest in your feed.

●Groups & Chat● Join groups based on your interests and chat with members. Meet other fellow cannabis fans and check out their profiles. Create a private chat with a friend!

●Safe & Secure● CannaBuzz was created by an experienced team with a background in both community management and as cannabis advocates. We built this place because we believe that the global cannabis community deserves a safe space online.

●Available on the Web ● Visit our website from your desktop computer, share your CannaBuzz content links with the world!
